---
title: Pork Belly and Chickpea Stew with Spring Greens and Smoked Paprika
description: These pork belly bacon rashers aren’t just good, they’re delicious.Our André delights in all things Spanish, so get ready to enjoy the subtle, sweet flavours of smoked paprika, spring greens and chickpea stew.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pork-belly-and-chickpea-stew-24-400e88c1.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/pork-belly-and-chickpea-stew-24-84dc195e.pdf
